    • Method Detail

      • convertRegistryObject

        public Map<String,Object> convertRegistryObject(RegistryObjectType registryObject)
        This method creates a Map representation of the RegistryObjectType provided. The following keys will be added to the map (Taken from EbrimConstants):

        CLASSIFICATION_KEY = "Classification"; EXTERNAL_IDENTIFIER_KEY = "ExternalIdentifier"; NAME_KEY = "Name"; DESCRIPTION_KEY = "Description"; VERSION_INFO_KEY = "VersionInfo"; SLOT = "Slot"; ID_KEY = "id"; HOME_KEY = "home"; LID_KEY = "Lid"; STATUS_KEY = "Status"; OBJECT_TYPE_KEY = "objectType";

        Uses: ClassificationWebConverter ExternalIdentifierWebConverter SlotWebConverter InternationalStringTypeHelper

        Parameters:
        registryObject - the RegistryObjectType to be converted into a map, null returns empty Map
        Returns:
        Map representation of the RegistryObjectType provided
